===Pronunciation===
   \Pail\
===Noun===

A [[vessel]] of wood or tin, etc., usually cylindrical and having
a bail, -- used esp. for carrying liquids, as water or milk,
etc.; a [[bucket]]. 

It may, or may not, have a cover. --Shak.

